      <title>英国金融公司寻求“大胆”改革以对抗华尔街的崛起</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/uk-finance-firms-seek-bold-reforms-counter-wall-st-ascendancy-2024-11-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伦敦金融超级大国地位面临新的挑战之际，英国金融业指望政策制定者能够出台一项规则改革，以增长为优先，防止业务被全球竞争对手抢走。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/uk-finance-firms-seek-bold-reforms-counter-wall-st-ascendancy-2024-11-13/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 13:11:25 GMT</pubDate>
